{{define "subject"}}Reset your {{.AppName}} password{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi {{.FirstName}},

We received a request to reset the password for your {{.AppName}} account.

Please send a request to the `PUT /api/v1/auth/password/reset` endpoint with the following JSON body to set your new password:
{
  "token": "{{.ResetToken}}",
  "user_id": "{{.UserID}}",
  "password": "YOUR_NEW_PASSWORD"
}

Please note that this is a one-time use token and it will expire in 15 minutes.

If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.

Thanks,

The {{.AppName}} Team
{{end}}

